text: Talmensky District () is an administrativeLaw #28-ZS and municipalLaw #54-ZS district (raion), one of the fifty-nine in Altai Krai, Russia. It is located in the north of the krai. The area of the district is . Its administrative center is the urban locality (a work settlement) of Talmenka. Population: The population of Talmenka accounts for 40.2% of the district's total population. ==References== ===Notes=== ===Sources=== * * Category:Districts of Altai Krai
